desc:Ring Modulate the two channels of a signal. Output a mono signal.
slider1:0<0,1,0.001>Mix L
slider2:0<0,1,0.001>Mix R

@slider
mix0=slider1;
mix1=slider2;

@sample
spl0=spl0*spl1 + (spl0 * mix0) + (spl0 * mix1);
spl1=spl0;

